universe:
Households located in eligible communities with at least a child between 36 and 59 months old and households located in eligible communities with at least a child between 0 and 35 months old and no other children between 36 and 59 months. 

Eligible communities are identified to meet the criteria for implementation of the program:
- The community is located in a rural area;
- The community already has a primary school;
- The community has more than 30 children in the age range of 3-5 years old;
- There was no other education program for children 3-5 years old in the community in the past 5 years.

